{"tid":429422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過發夢夢見屋企人死左喊到仆街","createTime":"2017-10-09T01:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T02:00:43.000Z","uid":52896,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80d0ddb5da3bfabed97c36719c4abc6231e17e41","tid":429422,"uid":52896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"同屋企人感情超好, 我好少喊<br />\n但每次發夢有屋企人死左起身都係流緊眼淚, 有時夢入面啲情節仆街啲既話會喊到腫哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚場夢有個呀哥為左救我笑住咁死, 具體情節一起身就唔記得, 但依家對眼紅緊<br />\n<br />\n講咁多廢話都係想講句<br />\n希望屋企人一直身體健康啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52229ff5984c3a2edc4167d851d38e97a6ee4c8","tid":429422,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a00dc958c42457e3fb502b4f99012925b88e53d","tid":429422,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未死右喊乜撚呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n右你老母 仲捉你唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da78862249d5637bff4a37a5d47cfdaabd3dcfc7","tid":429422,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未死右喊乜撚呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n右你老母 仲捉你唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聖人都會有錯<br />\n希望你比次機會肥絲老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec2e88e05d6c20d323b56a45ac2047b5e7af9c1","tid":429422,"uid":135067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:37:18.000Z","msg":"試過夢見屋企人死會sad一日同成日都好緊張<br />\n但又唔會喊"},{"pid":"5d708b515ec2933b22576de2577ff3e7ae0d25b9","tid":429422,"uid":41613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:43:19.000Z","msg":"完全唔會發呢d 夢"},{"pid":"c2424d04feddc12599b413e18cc95e49bab9c5ee","tid":429422,"uid":52288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc